title: Ep - 178 - CRAIG CONOVER FROM SOUTHERN CHARM
description:
Craig Conover from Bravo’s Southern Charm explains what transpired behind the scenes all season long between Austen and Madison. 


Podcast hosts Matt Marr and Jake Anthony help Kate review MTV’s Are You The One? 


Actor Doug Budin gives a rundown of his favorite shows on the Food Network.
